Silence::

She swallowed hard. A young bot was here. HERE! And it was not a
warrior, not a scout, not a battle technician, it was a very young
child bot.  Silence just froze and stared at the child. Fear was not
something she felt all that often. But now, fear for that young bot
life was all she knew.
